Text: Thanks 0vercast. Been looking forward to this one.

Thank you for bringing these shows to us, 0vercast. Your time and efforts are very much appreciated. Today is Sunday, 08 Nov 2009 - I truly hope that you have not abandoned this project. I know it takes time, and that gratitude is not expressed often - but for many people (myself included) these torrents are the only source for this show and I sincerely hope you will continue. Sending best regards.....and seeding as always. =)

Thx Xerox80...

I will be resuming uploads today.  Was out of town ;)
Sry for being inactive this month.  Will be back soon.
